<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbd0352d8-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c" identifier="/us/usc/t13/s81"><num value="81">§ 81.</num><heading> Statistics on apparel and textile industries</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall collect and publish quarterly statistics relating to domestic apparel and textile industries.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbd05c2d9-76cd-11f0-842a-a3c49cc8bf0c">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/99/467/s1/a">Pub. L. 99–467, § 1(a)</ref>, <date date="1986-10-14">Oct. 14, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1192">100 Stat. 1192</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
